{"tid":406822,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【屋邨孤兒仔】領展將拆售17個商場 市值145億","createTime":"2017-09-20T03:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T03:18:12.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af1175a762fd8c3b373201bdeef85caa81e48947","tid":406822,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505870547_44d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505870547_44d8.jpg&h=89e41642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505870355_6160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505870355_6160.jpg&h=6749964d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n領展（823）過往不斷拆售香港屋邨，今再傳出一份招標名單，合共出售17個商場物業，市值達145億元，有指屬意由1至2位買家收購，以確保管理質素，並會在12月截標。領展今早跌1%，報63.8元，暫成交7,771萬元。<br />\n<br />\n今次拆售共17個商場，以領展歷來最大規模出售資產，當中包括屯門、馬鞍山、葵涌區、九龍灣以及粉嶺區等等，而今次每個商場的市值均高過5億元，較以往出售的商場更加值錢。其中斥資5億元，屯門安定及友愛邨商場翻新後二合一的「H.A.N.D.S」商場，亦會出售，市值近29億元。另外，14年向嘉里建設（683）以13.8億收購的黃大仙現崇山商場亦會出售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57231937&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57231937%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170920&d=LWZ41l0dr1MEwd234I91EIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=df6b45c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57231937%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170920&h=f33daa61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57231937&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170920</a>"}]}